data.description: This 1901 Craftsman charmer boasts nostalgic high ceilings, pocket doors, woodwork, and clawfoot tub.  Modern conveniences include chefs kitchen, walk-in pantry, oversized solid walled rain shower, and upstairs laundry.  Enjoy the on demand tankless hot water heater, large corner lot, fully fenced backyard, hot tub, garden area complete with chicken coop, and secure off street parking able to accommodate RV/Boat. Uniquely this property offers ample storage with pull down steps to attic, unfinished basement, and outdoor sheds. Excellent location provides easy access to waterfront and downtown with view of Cascades. New windows let in abundant light and marine breeze.
